{"title":"微信小程序-text组件","date":"2023-04-22T03:52:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 22, 2023","L":"04/22/2023","MM-DD":"04-22"},"link":"2023/04/22/Web/微信小程序/component/常用组件/33-微信小程序-text组件","tags":["微信小程序"],"updated":"2023-04-22T10:02:04.205Z","content":"<h1 id=\"text\">text<a title=\"#text\" href=\"#text\"></a></h1>\n<p>官方文档地址：<a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/component/text.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/component/text.html</a></p>\n<p>text 组件：相当于 span，行内元素</p>\n<p>行内元素，我在 view(块级元素)当中编写了两个 text 组件，发现都在一行当中进行显示，证明了是行内元素。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span>我是 text 组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span>我是 text 组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img2023.cnblogs.com/blog/2105804/202304/2105804-20230422115346101-1983616252.png\" alt=\"image-20230422115345559\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"属性\">属性<a title=\"#属性\" href=\"#属性\"></a></h1>\n<p>?&gt;  user-select: 文本是否可选，该属性会使文本节点显示为 inline-block(selectable:文本是否可选 (已废弃))</p>\n<p>index.wxml:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span>我是 text 组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">user-select</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&#123;&#123;true&#125;&#125;&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">  &gt;</span>我是 text 组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>!&gt; 注意点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在小程序中，如果属性的取值是 boolean 类型, 如果要赋值为 true(真), 直接写上属性名称即可</li>\n</ul>\n<p>index.wxml:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span>我是 text 组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">user-select</span></span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">  &gt;</span>我是 text 组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>?&gt; space: 显示连续空格</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ensp：中文字符空格一半大小</li>\n<li>emsp：中文字符空格大小</li>\n<li>nbsp：根据字体设置的空格大小</li>\n</ul>\n<p>index.wxml:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">space</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ensp&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我是 text组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">space</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;emsp&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我是 text组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">space</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;nbsp&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我是 text组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>?&gt; decode: 是否解码</p>\n<p>index.wxml:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">decode</span>&gt;</span>我是<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">&amp;nbsp;</span>text组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"bug-&amp;-tip\">Bug &amp; Tip<a title=\"#bug-&amp;-tip\" href=\"#bug-&amp;-tip\"></a></h1>\n<ol>\n<li><code>tip</code>: decode可以解析的有 <code>&amp;nbsp;</code>、<code>&amp;lt;</code>、<code>&amp;gt;</code>、<code>&amp;amp;</code>、<code>&amp;apos;</code>、<code>&amp;ensp;</code>、<code>&amp;emsp;</code></li>\n<li><code>tip</code>: 各个操作系统的空格标准并不一致。</li>\n<li><code>tip</code>:<a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/component/text.html\" target=\"_blank\">text</a> 组件内只支持 <a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/component/text.html\" target=\"_blank\">text</a> 嵌套。</li>\n<li><code>tip</code>: 除了文本节点以外的其他节点都无法长按选中。</li>\n<li><code>bug</code>: 基础库版本低于 <code>2.1.0</code> 时， <a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/component/text.html\" target=\"_blank\">text</a> 组件内嵌的 <a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/component/text.html\" target=\"_blank\">text</a> style 设置可能不会生效。</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"组件差异\">组件差异<a title=\"#组件差异\" href=\"#组件差异\"></a></h1>\n<p>!&gt; 内联文本只能用 text 组件，不能用 view，如 <text> foo <text>bar</text> </text></p>\n<p>错误示例：</p>\n<p>index.wxml:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span>我是view<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">text</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img2023.cnblogs.com/blog/2105804/202304/2105804-20230422180202841-1960299980.png\" alt=\"image-20230422180202287\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"微信小程序-icon组件","link":"2023/04/22/Web/微信小程序/component/常用组件/34-微信小程序-icon组件"},"next":{"title":"微信小程序-view组件","link":"2023/04/22/Web/微信小程序/component/常用组件/32-微信小程序-view组件"},"plink":"http://example.com/2023/04/22/Web/微信小程序/component/常用组件/33-微信小程序-text组件/","toc":[{"id":"text","title":"text","index":"1"},{"id":"属性","title":"属性","index":"2"},{"id":"bug-&-tip","title":"Bug &amp; Tip","index":"3"},{"id":"组件差异","title":"组件差异","index":"4"}],"reading_time":"480 words in 3 min"}